<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Tastea - Blog</title>
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #1e1e1e;
            color: #e0e0e0;
            padding: 15px 0;
        }
        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #f39c12;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo img {
            max-width: 150px;
        }
        .nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .nav a {
            color: #e0e0e0;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
        .call-btn, .reserve-btn {
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border: 1px solid #f39c12;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .call-btn {
            color: #f39c12;
            background-color: transparent;
        }
        .reserve-btn {
            background-color: #f39c12;
            color: #121212;
        }
        .main-content {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #333333;
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: #333333;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .blog-posts {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .blog-post {
            width: 48%;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .blog-post img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .blog-post-content {
            padding: 15px;
        }
        .blog-post-meta {
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #888888;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .blog-post h3 {
            color: #333333;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .blog-post p {
            color: #666666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div class="header-content">
            <a href="#" class="call-btn">Call: xxx xxx xxx</a>
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="Screenshot 2024-10-02 022710.png" alt="The Tasteat Logo">
            </div>
            <a href="/reservation.ejs" class="reserve-btn">Reservation</a>
        </div>
        <nav class="nav">
            <a href="/homepage">Home</a>
            <a href="/review">Reviews</a>
            <a href="/ourmenu">Our Menu</a>
            <a href="/offer">Offers</a>
            <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main class="main-content">
        <h1>Be First Who Read News</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Explore the latest stories about our dishes, offers, events and future plan here.</p>

        <div class="blog-posts">
            <div class="blog-post">
                <img src="https://th.bing.com/th/id/OIP.TDKBZXOblk4L61v08dPUjQHaE5?w=255&h=180&c=7&r=0&o=5&dpr=1.3&pid=1.7" alt="US Cuisine">
                <div class="blog-post-content">
                    <div class="blog-post-meta">DELICIOUS • MARCH 28, 2024</div>
                    <h3>The Legend Of US Cuisine: The Story Of Hungry People</h3>
                    <p>Capitalize on low hanging fruit to identify a ballpark value added activity to beta test override the food quality.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="blog-post">
                <img src="https://assets.thehansindia.com/h-upload/2022/09/24/1313726-national-cooking-day.jpg">
                <div class="blog-post-content">
                    <div class="blog-post-meta">COOKING • MARCH 03,2024</div>
                    <h3>The Most Popular Delicious Food Of Mediterranean Cuisine</h3>
                    <p>Strategies on low hanging fruit to identify a ballpark value added activity to beta test override the food quality.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>